			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Be far away from Den, then use: oe readyattackonden\r\n- Activate the horn above Den gate to trigger Goblin raid\r\n- Side with Zevlor in dialogue and kill all goblins. \r\n(CTRL + Shift + K) or “killcombat”command is useful here \r\n- Talk to Marcoryl (ServantIntolerent002) down in the druid's underground Den at X:-470 Y:-11"
				},
